animeDescription: The anime centers around the daily life of two twin bear sisters: the orange-colored Lulu and the yellow-colored Lolo. The two take on new jobs and, despite the occasional failure and tears, give their best efforts.(Source: ANN)
animeRelated: ['Spin-off: Kuma no Gakkou: Jackie to Katie', 'Prequel: Ganbare! Lulu Lolo 2nd Season']
